summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2076, for the improvement of Brintnall Place, lying to the north of Northern Pacific right of way, extending from 9th Avenue Northeast to 14th Avenue Northeast; all in the City of Seattle, by grading, curbing and planking the same, to the full width; under Ordinance No. 21116 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
